.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-OPEN-PRIVATE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-open-private \- open an unannounced (private) channel
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-open-private
.I peer_id
.I sat
.SH DESCRIPTION
Opens a channel with
.I peer_id
for
.I sat
satoshis and sets
.B announce=false
so the channel is not broadcast to the gossip network.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"channel_id":..., "txid":..., "private":true}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-open (1),
.BR lightning-channel-open-dual (1)
